2003-12-13 15:09  Josef Spillner <dr_maux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* metaserv/metaserv/metaserv.c: - convert &s to &amp;s
	automatically when receiving data - in verbose mode, set logfile to
	stdout if not set

2003-12-09 15:11  Josef Spillner <dr_maux@users.sourceforge.net>

	* cmd-client/main.c: - addition of a modified 'checkonline'
	command: 'checknagios'
	
	This makes ggz-cmd compatible to plugins for Nagios
	(http://www.nagios.org).  People running Nagios (and many ISPs and
	companies do) can now seamlessly integrate checks for running GGZ
	servers.
	
	For the predecessor netsaint, it might look like:
	command[check_ggz]=/usr/lib/netsaint/plugins/ggz_cmd $HOSTNAME
	guestuser pass
	
	Josef

2003-09-20 15:36  Josef Spillner <dr_maux@users.sourceforge.net>

